pageContext.claim: “We've vastly expanded lower-cost health insurance plans. That's happening. And it's been an incredible success.”
pageContext.analysis: Trump appears to be referring to association health plans, but he exaggerates. The quality of AHPs will probably vary dramatically depending on who they’re targeting and states' regulations. They’re exempt from federal coverage requirements that apply to the individual and small group markets, but states have taken steps to varying degrees to regulate AHPs.
